@startuml
!define RECTANGLE class

RECTANGLE Bundle <<Bundle>>
RECTANGLE Composition <<ChEkmComposition>>
RECTANGLE Patient <<ChEkmPatientInitials>>
RECTANGLE Organization <<ChEkmOrganizationAuthor>>
RECTANGLE Organization <<ChEkmOrganizationLab>>
RECTANGLE ServiceRequest <<ChEkmServiceRequest>>
RECTANGLE Specimen <<ChEkmSpecimen>>
RECTANGLE Condition <<Condition>>
RECTANGLE Encounter <<Encounter>>
RECTANGLE Immunization <<Immunization>>

' Relaciones principales según el ejemplo InvasiveStreptococcusPneumoniae
Bundle -- Composition : entry
Bundle -- Patient : entry
Bundle -- Organization : entry
Bundle -- ServiceRequest : entry
Bundle -- Specimen : entry
Bundle -- Condition : entry
Bundle -- Encounter : entry
Bundle -- Immunization : entry

Composition -- Patient : subject
Composition -- Organization : author
Composition -- Encounter : encounter
Composition -- ServiceRequest : section[laboratory].entry
Composition -- Condition : section[diagnosis].entry
Composition -- Encounter : section[hospitalization].entry
Composition -- Immunization : section[immunization].entry
Composition -- Condition : section[risk-factors].entry

ServiceRequest -- Patient : subject
ServiceRequest -- Specimen : specimen
ServiceRequest -- Organization : performer

Specimen -- Patient : subject

Condition -- Patient : subject
Encounter -- Patient : subject

@enduml